Schneider May Buy Luminous for $800 Million, Wansquare Reports

-- B y   S t e v e   R h i n d s
-- 
2011-04-05T14:29:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-05/schneider-may-buy-luminous-for-800-million-wansquare-reports.html
Schneider Electric SA (SU)  is in advanced
talks to buy a 50 percent stake in India-based Luminous for
about $800 million, Wansquare reported on its website today,
citing unidentified bankers.    Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
